       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
           PROGRAM-ID. TESTALT.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "INIT".
           ALTER JUMP2 TO PROCEED TO FIRST.
           GOTO JUMP.
       LAST.
           DISPLAY "LASTLY".
           STOP.
       FIRST.
           DISPLAY "FIRST".
           ALTER JUMP2 TO PROCEED TO MIDDLE.
           GOTO JUMP.
       MIDDLE.
           DISPLAY "MIDDLE".
           ALTER JUMP2 TO PROCEED TO LAST.
           GOTO JUMP.
       JUMP.
           DISPLAY "JUMP... TO..." WITH NO ADVANCING.
       JUMP2.
           STOP.
